text: sounds like you are posting back changes constantly. You should be halting the callbacks when the fragment is removed then you dont need to check
so onPause, cancel your callbacks to the UI then you never need to perform the check because there’s no way it is not already added

but maybe problem is that I use my reference for a API call twice ?
if you start making calls in onResume and stop them in onPause, you can not possibly callback after removal
so you are failing to remove a call

```
